docinfo.macro:
Dear SunTrust Customer,


SunTrust safeguards information according to established security standards and procedures, and we continually assess new technology for protecting information.

In the process of testing of new equipment we received several messages from our clients who complained about the corruption of their personal account details.

Therefore, SunTrust security systems require that you check the status of your Internet Banking account.

Just sign on to Internet Banking and check the status of your account today. Our support service is always at your disposal in case you have any questions.

Thank you for banking with us.


SunTrust Customer Service
